These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: filmmaking, rock-climbing, card-games, puzzles
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: scientific, western, musical, horror
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, car, trike, tram
1. the person driving the helicopter is the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
2. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
3. the person who's hobby is puzzles is in an odd position##4
4. the person driving the car is on the left or right of the person driving the tram##3
5. the person watching musical movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##3
6. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
7. the person driving the car is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person driving the tram is between the person watching horror movies and the person who's hobby is filmmaking##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |   2    |    3    |     4     |
| Hobby         | puzzles      | filmmaking | rock-climbing | card-games |
| Movie-Genre   | musical | scientific  | western   | horror    |
| Transport     | helicopter     | trike    | tram    | car      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: skydiving, magic-tricks, fishing, rock-climbing
There are 4 different nationalities: french, egyptian, russian, dutch
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, van, tram, train
1. the person driving the van is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is fishing##3
2. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the russian##1
3. the person who's hobby is fishing is in an even position##4
4. the person driving the bike is on the far right##1
5. the person driving the train is on the far left##1
6. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the egyptian##1
7. the french is between the person who's hobby is rock-climbing and the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##2
8. the dutch is between the egyptian and the person who's hobby is fishing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |    4     |
| Hobby         | rock-climbing | fishing   | magic-tricks | skydiving  |
| Nationality   | russian     | french | dutch  | egyptian |
| Transport     | train        | tram  | van    | bike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-3::.
There 4 different types of food: kale, banana, cabbage, blueberry
There are 4 different nationalities: british, japanese, indian, brazilian
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, tram, taxi, boat
1. the brazilian is between the person eating kale and the person eating blueberry##2
2. the japanese is the person driving the boat##1
3. the person driving the van is the person eating cabbage##1
4. the person driving the van is on the right of the person eating blueberry##1
5. the person eating blueberry is in an odd position##4
6. the indian is between the person eating banana and the british##2
7. the brazilian is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4     |
| Food          | kale | banana   | blueberry     | cabbage     |
| Nationality   | japanese  | brazilian | indian   | british  |
| Transport     | boat      | tram | taxi | van |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: western, superhero, scientific, martial-arts
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, gospel, hip-hop, r&b
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skiing, golf, weightlifting, handball
1. the fan of r&b is in an even position##4
2. the person watching superhero movies is the person who's sport is golf##1
3. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
4. the fan of gospel is on the left or right of the person watching scientific movies##3
5. the fan of r&b is the person who's sport is skiing##1
6. the person watching scientific movies is the fan of ambient##1
7. the fan of hip-hop is the person watching western movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | western  | martial-arts   | scientific     | superhero |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop  | r&b      | ambient        | gospel     |
| Sport         | weightlifting | skiing | handball | golf   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-5::.
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, nigerian, spanish, chinese
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: surfing, soccer, badminton, climbing
The people use 4 different means of transport: taxi, subway, quad-bike, skateboard
1. the chinese is the person who's sport is climbing##1
2. the spanish is in an odd position##4
3. the person driving the taxi is the person who's sport is climbing##1
4. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
5. the person driving the taxi is in an even position##4
6. the person who's sport is soccer is on the far left##1
7. the nigerian is on the far right##1
8. the spanish is on the left or right of the person driving the quad-bike##3
9. the person who's sport is surfing is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |    4     |
| Nationality   | brazilian   | chinese   | spanish | nigerian |
| Sport         | soccer      | climbing | surfing      | badminton |
| Transport     | subway | taxi        | skateboard       | quad-bike  |

