.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-6::.
There 4 different types of food: banana, corn, lime, peas
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, dancing, filmmaking, video-games
4 different pets are kept: rabbit, snake, goldfish, goat
1. the person eating corn is in an odd position##4
2. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
3. the owner of the rabbit is the person eating corn##1
4. the person eating lime is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
5. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the far right##1
6. the person eating peas is on the left of the person eating corn##1
7. the person eating peas is in an even position##4
8. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |     3      |    4    |
| Food    | lime   | peas      | corn       | banana |
| Hobby   | board-games | video-games | filmmaking     | dancing |
| Pet     | goat     | snake  | rabbit | goldfish |

