.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-7::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, sprite, cola, coffee
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, crime, romance, family
4 different pets are kept: rat, ferret, bird, snake
1. the owner of the bird is the person watching adventure movies##1
2. the owner of the ferret is between the person watching family movies and the owner of the rat##2
3. the person watching family movies is the person drinking sprite##1
4. the person watching crime movies is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3
5. the person drinking mirinda is in an even position##4
6. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
7. the person watching adventure movies is the person drinking mirinda##1
8. the owner of the bird is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |       3       |     4      |
| Beverage      | cola   | coffee          | sprite | mirinda        |
| Movie-Genre   | romance     | crime | family   | adventure     |
| Pet           | rat | ferret         | snake         | bird |

