.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-8::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: photography, hiking, gardening, board-games
The people have 4 different jobs:  dancer, writer, firefighter, electrician
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, metal, hip-hop, jazz
1. the fan of jazz is on the left or right of the fan of hip-hop##3
2. the firefighter is the person who's hobby is photography##1
3. the electrician is the person who's hobby is gardening##1
4. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1
5. the fan of metal is between the dancer and the person who's hobby is photography##2
6. the fan of jazz is on the left or right of the firefighter##3
7. the person who's hobby is photography is in an even position##4
8. the person who's hobby is photography is between the person who's hobby is hiking and the person who's hobby is gardening##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |     4      |
| Hobby         | hiking | photography      | gardening       | board-games    |
| Job           | writer  | firefighter  | electrician | dancer |
| Music-Genre   | jazz      | hip-hop | metal         | classical    |

