.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-9::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, soy-milk, tea, lemonade
The people have 4 different jobs:  musician, designer, paramedic, nurse
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: sailing, parkour, golf, cycling
1. the musician is in an odd position##4
2. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the musician##3
3. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the musician##3
4. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
5. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person who's sport is golf##3
6. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the musician##1
7. the musician is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
8. the designer is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
9. the nurse is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |      3       |       4       |
| Beverage   | soy-milk         | almond-milk  | tea     | lemonade         |
| Job        | nurse | designer | musician | paramedic         |
| Sport      | parkour         | golf  | sailing   | cycling |

