.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-10::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, r&b, ambient, folk
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, american, italian, russian
4 different pets are kept: hamster, guinea-pig, bird, frog
 1. the owner of the bird is on the left or right of the fan of ambient##3
 2. the dutch is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the fan of r&b##1
 4. the italian is between the fan of r&b and the fan of d&b##2
 5. the owner of the frog is on the left or right of the fan of r&b##3
 6. the owner of the frog is the fan of ambient##1
 7. the russian is on the far right##1
 8. the fan of d&b is in an odd position##4
 9. the american is between the fan of folk and the fan of ambient##2
10. the owner of the bird is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | d&b  | ambient    | r&b | folk    |
| Nationality   | dutch | italian | american  | russian |
| Pet           | bird   | frog    | hamster        | guinea-pig   |

