.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-11::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, sprite, coffee, mirinda
The people have 4 different jobs:  project-manager, bartender, chef, security-guard
There are 4 different nationalities: nigerian, brazilian, malaysian, chinese
1. the person drinking milk is on the far left or far right##3
2. the bartender is on the left of the project-manager##1
3. the chinese is on the left or right of the chef##3
4. the bartender is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the project-manager##1
6. the chinese is on the right of the bartender##1
7. the brazilian is on the left of the bartender##1
8. the person drinking mirinda is on the left or right of the brazilian##3
9. the person drinking milk is on the left of the nigerian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Beverage      | milk                | mirinda  | sprite | coffee   |
| Job           | security-guard | bartender | project-manager   | chef |
| Nationality   | brazilian         | nigerian     | chinese     | malaysian |

