.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-12::.
There 4 different types of food: apple, cauliflower, carrot, asparagus
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: drama, animation, satire, martial-arts
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, funk, soul, pop
1. the person eating cauliflower is on the left of the person eating asparagus##1
2. the person eating carrot is on the far left##1
3. the fan of funk is on the left or right of the fan of pop##3
4. the person eating carrot is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
5. the fan of country is between the person watching martial-arts movies and the fan of pop##2
6. the person watching satire movies is in an even position##4
7. the person eating apple is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3    |    4    |
| Food          | carrot    | cauliflower  | asparagus  | apple |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | animation | drama | satire |
| Music-Genre   | soul    | country     | pop    | funk |

