.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-13::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, juice, milk, tea
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, american, french, nigerian
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, rabbit, guinea-pig, dog
1. the owner of the rabbit is between the person drinking milk and the canadian##2
2. the person drinking cola is on the far left or far right##3
3. the french is on the left or right of the owner of the guinea-pig##3
4. the owner of the dog is on the left of the american##1
5. the owner of the dog is in an odd position##4
6. the person drinking juice is on the left or right of the owner of the guinea-pig##3
7. the canadian is on the left or right of the nigerian##3
8. the french is the person drinking cola##1
9. the nigerian is between the owner of the guinea-pig and the owner of the goldfish##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3    |     4     |
| Beverage      | cola | milk      | juice  | tea    |
| Nationality   | french   | american | nigerian | canadian |
| Pet           | dog      | guinea-pig       | rabbit   | goldfish      |

