.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-14::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: filmmaking, fishing, puzzles, video-games
There are 4 different nationalities: mexican, thai, french, american
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skateboarding, climbing, biathlon, volleyball
1. the person who's hobby is puzzles is in an even position##4
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is between the person who's hobby is video-games and the person who's sport is skateboarding##2
3. the person who's sport is climbing is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who's hobby is video-games is in an even position##4
5. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
6. the american is between the person who's sport is skateboarding and the mexican##2
7. the person who's sport is climbing is on the far right##1
8. the thai is in an even position##4
9. the person who's sport is skateboarding is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3     |     4      |
| Hobby         | filmmaking    | puzzles | fishing  | video-games  |
| Nationality   | french | thai       | american | mexican |
| Sport         | biathlon   | skateboarding      | volleyball | climbing       |

