4. the person drinking mirinda is the person watching western movies##1
5. the person drinking mirinda is on the far left##1
6. the person watching disaster movies is the owner of the snake##1
7. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
8. the owner of the hedgehog is the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3    |   4    |
