The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, rowing, ice-hockey, weightlifting
The people use 4 different means of transport: roller, subway, tram, taxi
1. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3
2. the person who's sport is cycling is in an even position##4
3. the person driving the taxi is on the far left##1
4. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3
5. the person drinking sprite is between the person driving the subway and the person who's sport is ice-hockey##2
6. the person driving the roller is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
7. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
8. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage    | soy-milk    | sprite     | fanta    | 7up        |
| Sport       | ice-hockey   | cycling | rowing | weightlifting |
| Transport   | taxi | tram      | subway    | roller   |

