4. the person eating strawberry is on the far left or far right##3
5. the malaysian is on the left of the french##1
6. the person eating strawberry is in an odd position##4
7. the pakistani is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person eating eggplant is the person watching drama movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
