.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-20::.
There 4 different types of food: strawberry, plum, asparagus, eggplant
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, skydiving, magic-tricks, photography
4 different pets are kept: rabbit, hedgehog, snake, lizard
1. the person eating strawberry is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's hobby is photography is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the rabbit is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##3
4. the person eating asparagus is on the far left##1
5. the person eating plum is between the person who's hobby is photography and the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##2
6. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
7. the owner of the snake is on the right of the person eating strawberry##1
8. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the person eating plum##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |   3    |      4      |
| Food    | asparagus    | plum    | strawberry  | eggplant |
| Hobby   | photography | skydiving | rock-climbing | magic-tricks      |
| Pet     | hedgehog   | rabbit        | lizard   | snake       |

 